: : Rodimus Prime/Kup/Lunekill/Darkangel/DeathStar : :

Rodimus Prime looked up just in time to see Kup and the other Maximal&#39;s shots strike Lunekill at her core.

Lunekill&#39;s face showed nothing but pain and horror and her core exploded blowing her apart from within. Her last words were haunting, however.

Lunekill: We are merely the first wave, soon you&#39;ll face.... UNICRON!

The battle was over and, although damaged, the Maximals and their base had survived.

Rodimus, Kup and Darkangel, who had come out of stasis, all made their way to where Lunekill had just died.

Kup: Lads, I feel we have a problem...

Darkangel: Now, Rodimus Prime, will you commit the Maximals to Tyrael&#39;s alliance? Now that you know exactly what you will be dealing with.

Rodimus Prime: Why didn&#39;t you just tell me the truth, Tripred. You said a great force was coming but you never told me it was Unicron!

Darkangel: My orders were not to inform you of that as of yet. Now you know and it makes no difference. Will you join the Tripredacus and Predacons in this venture? Will you help supply parts for our anti-Unicron weapon?

Rodimus looks down, thinking it over. What other choice was there? This was the only way to protect his Maximals....

He looks over at Nightlight and thinks about Elita.

... And his family.

Rodimus Prime: Yes. I here by ally the Maximals with the Tripredacus and Predacons for this, and only this, project.

Darkangel: Great! Star preparing parts. I&#39;ll go inform Tyrael and then return to help. Beast mode!

Darkangel transforms to his bat form and flies off. Flight was difficult since his wings had been wounded in the battle.

*************************************************************************************

: : DeathStar : : 

At the selected location for the &quot;uber gun,&quot; DeathStar had finished setting up the hovor platform and other parts that he had brought. Now he needed a team of workers from the factions and the weapon parts to start construction on the gun.

Tyrael would need to be informed of the progress. With the communication jammers still in place he would have to go himself.

To guard the huge platform DeathStar activates a force field around it.

DeathStar: Flight mode!

The TM2 Tripredacus agent transformes to his flight mode and heads for the Tripred base.




